<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الكَلِمَةُ الطَّيِّبَةُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">قَالَ النَّبِيُّ صلى الله عليه وسلم:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«الكَلِمَةُ الطَّيِّبَةُ صَدَقَةٌ»</span> <span style="color:#008000">(١)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
